"""Type stubs for State.

Auto-generated methods installed by @add_accessors at runtime (see
schemas.py) are declared here so static type checkers and IDEs can resolve
them. Hand-written methods on State are also declared here, since a .pyi
replaces the .py for type-checking purposes.

A meta-test asserts every public method on State has a matching stub here,
with the same async/sync kind and the same signature.
"""
